Poppy , also known as That Poppy , is an American singer , songwriter , and YouTube personality .
Raised in Nashville , Tennessee , she moved to Los Angeles in 2014 to pursue a musical career , where she signed with Island Records and released her debut EP , Bubblebath -LRB- 2016 -RRB- .
In late 2016 , she became the face of Sanrio 's `` Hello Sanrio '' collection .